The Court Mu oversees important Muist rituals at court.

Entrusted with the brewing of alchemical potions and related matters, the Court Alchemist is in a great position to help with a variety of ailments... or to poison those foolish enough to trust them...
The Chief Gardener is responsible for tending to the palace gardens, keeping them safe from pests and intruders and also keeping the flowers blooming regardless of drought or downpour.
